name: Maven POMs (Moved to GitHub issues)
description: This JIRA project is for issues regarding the parent POMs used by Apache projects (component: asf) and Maven itself (components: maven, maven-plugins and maven-shared-components). It is also used to track issues for the resource bundle used by Apache projects (component: apache-jar-resource-bundle).
